text = "GODOT VOXEL TEST SCENE

This scene requires godot_voxel GDExtension to be installed.

INSTALLATION:
1. Upgrade to Godot 4.4.1+ or 4.5+
2. Download GDExtension from: https://github.com/Zylann/godot_voxel/releases
3. Extract to project root
4. Enable plugin in Project Settings

SETUP FOR THIS SCENE:
1. Add VoxelTerrain node as child of this scene
2. Set VoxelTerrain.generator to VoxelTerrainGenerator script
3. Create VoxelBlockyLibrary with block types
4. Set VoxelTerrain.mesher to VoxelMesherBlocky with library
5. Add VoxelViewer as child of Camera3D

See docs/GODOT_VOXEL_INTEGRATION.md for details."

